These are 4 very simple examples that show some of the abilities that DGL provides

CCallbackHelix - A simple spinning helix using the C callbacks in DGL
coinfly        - A simple model viewing program for .iv and .wrl files using Coin3D
dosgfly        - A simple model viewing program for .osg and other files Open Scene Graph loads
quad           - An example of how to load VTK content into DGL
